                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>One billion people impacted. Millions of workdays missed. Countless events skipped. The toll of migraine adds up. But so does progress in care.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
